#. <CLT 04>ジャバウォック公園…<CLT>
msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Here we are at the music room...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>海に囲まれた公園の真ん中には、<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>５体の架空の動物をかたどった銅像がある。<CLT>
msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>But it feels less like a room, and more like a full-on\n"
"music *hall*.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>俺たちの他に人影はないみたいだけど…<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>さてどうしようか？<CLT>
msgctxt "0003"
msgid "I'm a big fan of music."
msgstr ""

#. とりあえず座ろうか
msgctxt "0004"
msgid "Hmm... I'm pretty much take it or leave it."
msgstr ""

#. そうだね。
#. あっちの木陰の方に行こうか。
msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"I don't really listen to the radio or anything, so I\n"
"have no idea what's popular."
msgstr ""

#. …うーん、木陰に並んで座っておしゃべりって
#. かなりそれっぽいよね？
msgctxt "0006"
msgid "Hey, Makoto! Why don't you make me a mixtape?"
msgstr ""

#. あ、でも私、黙って座ってるとたぶん
#. すぐ寝ちゃうと思うから…
msgctxt "0007"
msgid "Can you play any instruments?"
msgstr ""

#. 頑張って色々お話しようね。
msgctxt "0008"
msgid "Umm...just the recorder. At, like, a 4th grade level."
msgstr ""

#. 散歩でもするか
msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"For a while I was super obsessed with the piano and\n"
"wanted to take lessons and stuff..."
msgstr ""

#. あ、いいね。
#. この辺もまだあんまり探検してないし。
msgctxt "0010"
msgid "But in the end, I just loved sports more."
msgstr ""

#. …あ、でもこれってデートだったっけ。
msgctxt "0011"
msgid "Does that, like...make me stupid?"
msgstr ""

#. 探検より色々お話しなくちゃだね。
#. ええと…どうしよう…
msgctxt "0012"
msgid "I've always wanted to see some live music."
msgstr ""

#. ご趣味は？
#. …とか聞けばいいのかな？
msgctxt "0013"
msgid "Whaaat!?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>別に探検でもいい気はするけどな…<CLT>
msgctxt "0014"
msgid ""
"Y-You're a total delinquent! Going out late at night,\n"
"messing around with troublemakers! Bad Makoto!"
msgstr ""

#. いい景色だな
msgctxt "0015"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. うーん…確かに悪くはないけど、
#. 割と普通だと思うな。
msgctxt "0016"
msgid "I wanna do some karaoke."
msgstr ""

#. …あ、ごめん。
#. なんか気の利かないこと言ったね。
msgctxt "0017"
msgid ""
"Oh, that sounds like fun! I feel super charged up when\n"
"I finish up a good karaoke session!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>気が利かないのはむしろ俺のほうだよな…<CLT>
msgctxt "0018"
msgid "I really suck at singing, though..."
msgstr ""

#. 昼寝に良さそうだ
msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"When I really get into it, I just start getting\n"
"louder. Pretty soon it's not even singing!"
msgstr ""

#. うん、特にあの木陰とか、
#. 昼寝のためにあるような場所だと思うよ。
msgctxt "0020"
msgid "The mic just gets all \"squeeeeEEEEE!\""
msgstr ""

#. まぁ、私はどこでも寝られるけど
#. どうせならあったかくて柔らかいほうがいいしね。
msgctxt "0021"
msgid "It happens every time!"
msgstr ""

#. あ、でも一緒にお昼寝するのは
#. デートのうちに入るのかな？
msgctxt "0022"
msgid "That's happened to you though, right!?"
msgstr ""

#. 私は…そうしたいなって思うけど…
msgctxt "0023"
msgid "I'd love to hear Sayaka sing sometime..."
msgstr ""

#. …どうかな？
msgctxt "0024"
msgid ""
"Ooh yeah, she could do a super exclusive pop sensation\n"
"performance! That's, like, ultra luxury!"
msgstr ""

#. あの像、気になるな…
msgctxt "0025"
msgid ""
"I mean, just having a musical superstar for a\n"
"classmate is already something out of a movie..."
msgstr ""

#. うん…なんていうか…妙に存在感のある像だよね。
msgctxt "0026"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Well...I think just having you here is good enough for\n"
"me.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 島の秘密を解く暗号とかになってるのかな？
#. それともやっぱり回したりずらしたりかな？
msgctxt "0027"
msgid "There's not much to do here..."
msgstr ""

#. じゃなかったら、雷が落ちると動き出すとか…
msgctxt "0028"
msgid ""
"Haha, yeah! It's cuz neither of us are huge experts\n"
"on like, arts and entertainment, right?"
msgstr ""

#. うーん、考え出すとキリがないね。
msgctxt "0029"
msgid "So should we just, like...quietly sneak away?"
msgstr ""

#. 木登りでもするか
msgctxt "0030"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. …すごいね。
#. 日向くん、木登りできるんだ。
msgctxt "0031"
msgid "Wanna try singing together with everyone?"
msgstr ""

#. 私もやってみたいけど…
#. たぶん、途中でゲージが切れると思うな…
msgctxt "0032"
msgid "Oh, yeah! That sounds awesome!"
msgstr ""

#. あの像を壊すと…
msgctxt "0033"
msgid ""
"After months of practice, we sync our timing and\n"
"performance perfectly, then take on Koshien!"
msgstr ""

#. あ、それは私もちょっと考えてた。
msgctxt "0034"
msgid "Wait...that's for baseball, huh?"
msgstr ""

#. 動かすギミックにしては
#. ちょっと大きすぎると思うんだよね。
msgctxt "0035"
msgid ""
"Still, anything's fun if we can do it as a group!\n"
"It's like another notch in the belt of youth!"
msgstr ""

#. 破壊できるほどの武器は装備してないから、
#. どこかに爆発物があるのかな。
msgctxt "0036"
msgid "This is a pretty nice piano."
msgstr ""

#. あ、でも島の象徴っぽい像だし、
#. 破壊の呪文みたいなほうが正解かな…
msgctxt "0037"
msgid ""
"It looks pretty expensive... I wanna touch it, but I\n"
"don't wanna leave fingerprints."
msgstr ""

#. デートにも謎解きが用意されてるなんて
#. やっぱり日向くんと一緒は面白いなぁ。
msgctxt "0038"
msgid ""
"It's like, so nice that I wouldn't wanna use it, but\n"
"if you don't use it, what's the point?"
msgstr ""

#. あの像を動かすと…
msgctxt "0039"
msgid "Agh...infinite thought loop!"
msgstr ""

#. 無難に地下への入り口とかかなぁ？
msgctxt "0040"
msgid "You think this room might be haunted?"
msgstr ""

#. でももしかしたら移動じゃなくて、
#. 回転させるほうかもしれないし…
msgctxt "0041"
msgid "I-I don't wanna talk about it! Knock it off!"
msgstr ""

#. どこかでフラグを立ててからじゃないと
#. 動かないってパターンもあるよね。
msgctxt "0042"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
